data.description: Welcome to 26 Lilac Lane! Beautifully situated on a corner lot in Rose Hill Manor, this colonial is the total package. Upon entering you’ll be greeted by a 2-story foyer with a formal living room and dining room. Moving through the foyer brings you to a beautiful eat-in-kitchen with stainless steel appliances, tile flooring, tile backsplash and granite countertops. Off the kitchen, laminate wood floors bring you into the family room with a wood burning fireplace and glass sliding doors leading to the beautifully landscaped backyard. A powder room and laundry room complete the first floor. Upstairs, four sizable bedrooms and full bath await including the primary bedroom with laminate wood floors and an ensuite with soaking jetted tub, double vanity and shower. Situated on almost half an acre, the fully fenced backyard is your own perfect oasis featuring a paver patio and deck. Additional features include a 1-year home warranty, new HVAC (2022) and water heater (2022). With nearby schools and amenities, this colonial home is a must-see!
